Package: dada2rs
Type: Package
Title: Drop-in replacement for dada2 backed by a Rust core
Version: 0.1.0
Author: dada2-rs contributors
Maintainer: dada2-rs contributors <noreply@example.com>
Description: Provides filterAndTrim, learnErrors, derepFastq, dada,
    mergePairs, makeSequenceTable, and removeBimeraDenovo using a
    high-performance Rust implementation via extendr.
    Compatible with the original R dada2 API (Callahan et al. 2016).
License: MIT
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: Cargo (>= 1.78), Rust toolchain, libbz2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
